could it have happened? No, no. Okay. There's just

10:55.582 --> 10:57.164
so many spots open. Yeah, I'm not... I'm just 
wondering about this. You're asking questions

11:01.470 --> 11:03.953
I'm answering. Just so you know, there was nothing 
