Tell me about when you learned that you were going 
to be promoted to brigadier general. How'd you

12:16.297 --> 12:19.581
find out?

12:24.488 --> 12:25.289
Let me see. How did I find that

12:25.389 --> 12:34.861
out? I think I got a call from

12:35.001 --> 12:45.615
a general someplace on the, well, maybe 
Washington. Probably Washington. Got a call from

12:49.039 --> 12:50.361
him. Just called me at my headquarter there at... 
