14:24.205 --> 14:40.589
follow them and they'll snoot and they'll do 
everything, you know, to find out when they're

14:24.205 --> 14:40.589
going to be out, you know, and they listen and do 
everything you can to find out things. But I knew

14:41.611 --> 14:47.980
the announcement was imminent and, you know, I was 
waiting and then, of course, I got this earlier

14:48.533 --> 14:57.223
call from one of the, I think it was the Pentagon, no 
question it was the Pentagon, but at any rate,

14:48.533 --> 14:57.223
someplace on the East Coast, he called me and 
congratulated me. I'm pretty sure that was his

14:57.243 --> 14:59.065
first indication. The first thing I did was went in 
my office and called Doris and told her about it.

