people. This is a tremendous leap in 
responsibility for us. How'd you like all the

26:01.795 --> 26:10.207
additional

26:01.795 --> 26:10.207
responsibility? Well, it's a challenge. I liked 
it. I had to work. I accepted it. And my wife

26:25.201 --> 26:30.446
detected the true dedication and the work and my 
position. You know, it involved her and I found it

